commits.message:
Generator for internal bindings for admin services EUCA-4283

Run using:

( cd eucalyptus/clc
  ant jar # or a 'make' is fine, too.
  ../devel/groovy.sh ./modules/msgs/src/main/java/generate-xsd.groovy
)

This will produce a number of .wsdl files.  Today that is:
ComponentService.wsdl
ConfigurationService.wsdl
Empyrean.wsdl
PropertiesService.wsdl

Each contains the WSDL for the service along with annotations that
detail the Query protocol parameter names.
